Insider Activity


Individual




Rona Alison Fairhead



Ms. Rona A. Fairhead is Chairman at BBC Trust, Independent Director at PepsiCo, Inc., Independent Non-Executive Director at HSBC Holdings Plc, Non-Executive Director at Spencer Stuart, Inc., and a Member-Library Visiting Committee at University of Cambridge. She is on the Board of Directors at PepsiCo, Inc., Cabinet Office, HSBC Holdings Plc, and Spencer Stuart, Inc.
Ms. Fairhead was previously employed as Chairman by Interactive Data Corp., Chairman by Financial Times Group Ltd., Non-Executive Director by The Economist Group Ltd., Non-Executive Director by The Economist Newspaper Ltd., Non-Executive Director by The Economist Newspaper Group, Inc., Executive Director by Pearson Plc, Executive Vice President-Strategy & Group Control by Imperial Chemical Industries Plc, EVP, Head-Group Control & Strategy by Imperial Chemical Industries Plc, and Non-Executive Chairman by HSBC North America Holdings, Inc.
She received her graduate degree from St Catharine's College Cambridge and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



