Rona Alison Fairhead



Rona Alison Fairhead was Born in August, 1961 (56 years old)  a resident of 80 Strand, , London, , WC2R 0RL (England) having Britsh nationality and was first ever appointed as Director in Pearson Group Pension Trustee Limited on Tuesday 06 November 2001 and as per the records from Registrar of Companies last appointment was in Mergermarket Limited as Director on Friday 29 September 2006 and currently holding positions as Director Rona Alison Fairhead was appointed in over 23 companies and currently holding positions in over 0 Companies.













